ch-affektiven Beziehungen.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 16. Mai 2019) 0aEconomics in literature. 0aEmotions in literature. 0aRomanticism. 4aAffect. 4aAffekt. 4aEconomy. 4aModerne. 4aModernity. 4aPoetics. 4aPoetik. 4aÖkonomie. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / General.2bisacsh1 aHindemith, Gesine, eeditor.1 aStöferle, Dagmar, eeditor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2018z9783110603187oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97831104776100 cprintz978311047744340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110479638423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110479638.jpg  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DKUb2018